long.ar:
WHAT

Presto Map lead extractor helps you extract business listings from Bing Maps and OpenStreetMap.

FOR WHOM AND WHY

Is your business targeting small businesses: Restaurants, bars, grocery stores, garages, hairdressers, small clothing shops, art galleries, and so on?

If that's the case, you've probably found yourself spending COUNTLESS hours browsing the Web building a prospection file. Emails, websites, addresses, and phone numbers are scattered all over the place, and, if not an intern, YOU will have to spend precious time gathering them before you can even get started prospecting.

This is the modern equivalent of "Take the phone book, go to 'A' and start dialing".

FEATURES

Using this software and data from maps, you can:
* Find leads literally at any place in the world
* Quickly filter and analyze leads in Excel 

The app is not magic. It extracts all available data from Online maps. Without this software, you can do it manually or hire a virtual assistant to do this job.

Functionality:
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Bing maps 
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Open Street maps (OSM) 
ğŸ“Š Download as Excel with proper column types or in CSV
âœ¨ The resulting spreadsheet contains 22 columns including phone numbers, venue name, and address (both English and localized variants), website, average rating, etc.

Please note: this app is freemium software. You can use a limited version for free or upgrade for unlimited usage. The download feature is limited to the recent 40 records. 

NOW TO USE ON BING MAPS

1. Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2. Search for something on Bing Maps - http://bing.com/maps/
3. See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
4. Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup

NOW TO USE ON OPEN STREET MAPS

1) Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2) Go to https://overpass-turbo.eu/ 
You can use any Oversee gateway - https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API 
3) Perform search by pressing â€œRunâ€ - the query language is described there: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API
4) See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
5) Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup
5.1) Clear results if you donâ€™t need them and want to collect from scratch

ISSUES

If you see that your queries are slow on the web it could break Presto functionality.

GET SUPPORT

Support email: support@presto-maps-scraper.com

This product are not endorsed by or affiliated with the OpenStreetMap Foundation.

The Bing is a trademark of the Microsoft Corporation. This product are not endorsed by or affiliated with the Microsoft Corporation.

Introducing Google Maps Lead Extractor: The Ultimate Tool for Finding Local Leads!

Are you looking to target small businesses such as restaurants, bars, grocery stores, garages, hairdressers, small clothing shops, and art galleries? With Google Maps Lead Extractor, you can quickly and easily extract business listings from OpenStreetMap and save yourself countless hours of manual labor!

Google Maps Lead Extractor is the perfect solution for finding local leads. With this powerful tool, you can: 

â€¢ Quickly and easily find leads from any location around the world 
â€¢ Easily filter and analyze leads in Excel 
â€¢ Extract listings from Open Street maps (OSM) 
â€¢ Download leads as Excel with proper column types or in CSV 
â€¢ Download records collected with the extensionâ€™s popup 
â€¢ Have access to 22 columns including phone numbers, venue name, and address (both English and localized variants), website, and average rating 

Using Google Maps Lead Extractor is simple! All you have to do is click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar, find the Google Maps Lead Extractor icon and pin it to the toolbar for quick access. Then, you can go to https://overpass-turbo.eu/ and perform a search by pressing â€œRun.â€ Youâ€™ll then be able to download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup. 

Google Maps Lead Extractor is a freemium software, so you can use a limited version for free or upgrade for unlimited usage. However, please note that the download feature is limited to the recent 40 records. 

If you encounter any issues while using Google Maps Lead Extractor, you can always contact their support team at support@presto-maps-scraper.com. 

Please note that the OpenStreetMap is a trademark of the OpenStreetMap Foundation, and is used with their permission. Google Maps Lead Extractor is not endorsed by or affiliated with the OpenStreetMap Foundation. 

Stop wasting your time manually searching for local leads. With Google Maps Lead Extractor, you can quickly and easily find leads from any location around the world. Download Google Maps Lead Extractor today and save yourself countless hours of manual labor!

WHAT

Presto Map lead extractor helps you extract business listings from Bing Maps and OpenStreetMap.

FOR WHOM AND WHY

Is your business targeting small businesses: Restaurants, bars, grocery stores, garages, hairdressers, small clothing shops, art galleries, and so on?

If that's the case, you've probably found yourself spending COUNTLESS hours browsing the Web building a prospection file. Emails, websites, addresses, and phone numbers are scattered all over the place, and, if not an intern, YOU will have to spend precious time gathering them before you can even get started prospecting.

This is the modern equivalent of "Take the phone book, go to 'A' and start dialing".

FEATURES

Using this software and data from maps, you can:
* Find leads literally at any place in the world
* Quickly filter and analyze leads in Excel 

The app is not magic. It extracts all available data from Online maps. Without this software, you can do it manually or hire a virtual assistant to do this job.

Functionality:
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Bing maps 
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Open Street maps (OSM) 
ğŸ“Š Download as Excel with proper column types or in CSV
âœ¨ The resulting spreadsheet contains 22 columns including phone numbers, venue name, and address (both English and localized variants), website, average rating, etc.

Please note: this app is freemium software. You can use a limited version for free or upgrade for unlimited usage. The download feature is limited to the recent 40 records. 

NOW TO USE ON BING MAPS

1. Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2. Search for something on Bing Maps - http://bing.com/maps/
3. See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
4. Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup

NOW TO USE ON OPEN STREET MAPS

1) Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2) Go to https://overpass-turbo.eu/ 
You can use any Oversee gateway - https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API 
3) Perform search by pressing â€œRunâ€ - the query language is described there: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API
4) See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
5) Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup
5.1) Clear results if you donâ€™t need them and want to collect from scratch

ISSUES

If you see that your queries are slow on the web it could break Presto functionality.

GET SUPPORT

Support email: support@presto-maps-scraper.com

Introducing Presto Google Maps Scraper - the revolutionary tool to help you quickly and easily find business listings from Google Maps! 

With Presto Google Maps Scraper, you can save COUNTLESS hours of time and effort when it comes to finding leads for your business. Whether you are targeting small businesses like restaurants, bars, grocery stores, garages, hairdressers, small clothing shops, art galleries, or any other type of business, Presto Google Maps Scraper has you covered. 

Using Presto Google Maps Scraper, you can: 

* Find leads from any place in the world 
* Quickly and easily filter and analyze leads in Excel 
* Extract listings from Google Maps 
* Download leads in either Excel with proper column types or in CSV 
* Access a spreadsheet containing 22 columns, including phone numbers, venue name, address (both English and localized variants), website, average rating, and more! 

Using Presto Google Maps Scraper is easy - simply click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar, find the Prestoâ€™s icon, and pin it to the toolbar for quick access. Then, go to https://overpass-turbo.eu/ and use the query language described in the link to perform a search. You can also use any Oversee gateway - https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API. As you search, you can watch the number of results increase over the toolbar icon. Finally, download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup. 

Presto Google Maps Scraper is a freemium software, so you can use a limited version for free or upgrade for unlimited usage. Please note that the download feature is limited to the recent 40 records.

WHAT

Presto Map lead extractor helps you extract business listings from Bing Maps and OpenStreetMap.

FOR WHOM AND WHY

Is your business targeting small businesses: Restaurants, bars, grocery stores, garages, hairdressers, small clothing shops, art galleries, and so on?

If that's the case, you've probably found yourself spending COUNTLESS hours browsing the Web building a prospection file. Emails, websites, addresses, and phone numbers are scattered all over the place, and, if not an intern, YOU will have to spend precious time gathering them before you can even get started prospecting.

This is the modern equivalent of "Take the phone book, go to 'A' and start dialing".

FEATURES

Using this software and data from maps, you can:
* Find leads literally at any place in the world
* Quickly filter and analyze leads in Excel 

The app is not magic. It extracts all available data from Online maps. Without this software, you can do it manually or hire a virtual assistant to do this job.

Functionality:
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Bing maps 
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Open Street maps (OSM) 
ğŸ“Š Download as Excel with proper column types or in CSV
âœ¨ The resulting spreadsheet contains 22 columns including phone numbers, venue name, and address (both English and localized variants), website, average rating, etc.

Please note: this app is freemium software. You can use a limited version for free or upgrade for unlimited usage. The download feature is limited to the recent 40 records. 

NOW TO USE ON BING MAPS

1. Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2. Search for something on Bing Maps - http://bing.com/maps/
3. See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
4. Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup

NOW TO USE ON OPEN STREET MAPS

1) Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2) Go to https://overpass-turbo.eu/ 
You can use any Oversee gateway - https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API 
3) Perform search by pressing â€œRunâ€ - the query language is described there: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API
4) See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
5) Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup
5.1) Clear results if you donâ€™t need them and want to collect from scratch

ISSUES

If you see that your queries are slow on the web it could break Presto functionality.

GET SUPPORT

Support email: support@presto-maps-scraper.com

DISCLAIMER

The OpenStreemMap is a trademark of the OpenStreetMap Foundation, and is used with their permission.
This product are not endorsed by or affiliated with the OpenStreetMap Foundation.

The Bing is a trademark of the Microsoft Corporation. This product are not endorsed by or affiliated with the Microsoft Corporation.

Ang app ay hindi magic. Ito ay lumalabas sa lahat ng data mula sa online maps. Nang walang software na ito, maaari mong gawin ito manually o mag-hire ng virtual assistant upang gawin ito.

1) Mag-click sa "puzzle" icon sa toolbar. Hanapin ang icon ng Presto at i-pin sa toolbar para sa mabilis na access.

Kung makikita mo na ang iyong mga query ay mabagal sa web, ito ay maaaring maging sanhi ng pagkabigo sa pagganap ng Presto.

* Quickly filter and analyze leads in Excel

WHAT

Presto Map lead extractor helps you extract business listings from Bing Maps and OpenStreetMap.

FOR WHOM AND WHY

Is your business targeting small businesses: Restaurants, bars, grocery stores, garages, hairdressers, small clothing shops, art galleries, and so on?

If that's the case, you've probably found yourself spending COUNTLESS hours browsing the Web building a prospection file. Emails, websites, addresses, and phone numbers are scattered all over the place, and, if not an intern, YOU will have to spend precious time gathering them before you can even get started prospecting.

This is the modern equivalent of "Take the phone book, go to 'A' and start dialing".

FEATURES

Using this software and data from maps, you can:
* Find leads literally at any place in the world
* Quickly filter and analyze leads in Excel 

The app is not magic. It extracts all available data from Online maps. Without this software, you can do it manually or hire a virtual assistant to do this job.

Functionality:
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Bing maps 
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Open Street maps (OSM) 
ğŸ“Š Download as Excel with proper column types or in CSV
âœ¨ The resulting spreadsheet contains 22 columns including phone numbers, venue name, and address (both English and localized variants), website, average rating, etc.

Please note: this app is freemium software. You can use a limited version for free or upgrade for unlimited usage. The download feature is limited to the recent 40 records. 

NOW TO USE ON BING MAPS

1. Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2. Search for something on Bing Maps - http://bing.com/maps/
3. See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
4. Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup

NOW TO USE ON OPEN STREET MAPS

1) Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2) Go to https://overpass-turbo.eu/ 
You can use any Oversee gateway - https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API 
3) Perform search by pressing â€œRunâ€ - the query language is described there: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API
4) See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
5) Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup
5.1) Clear results if you donâ€™t need them and want to collect from scratch

ISSUES

If you see that your queries are slow on the web it could break Presto functionality.

GET SUPPORT

Support email: support@presto-maps-scraper.com

DISCLAIMER

The OpenStreemMap is a trademark of the OpenStreetMap Foundation, and is used with their permission.
This product are not endorsed by or affiliated with the OpenStreetMap Foundation.

The Bing is a trademark of the Microsoft Corporation. This product are not endorsed by or affiliated with the Microsoft Corporation.

Presto Map Lead Extractor adalah sebuah alat yang membantu Anda untuk mengambil daftar bisnis dari OpenStreetMap. 
Apa yang Dimaksud dengan "FOR WHOM AND WHY"?
Apakah bisnis Anda menargetkan bisnis kecil: Restoran, bar, toko sayuran, bengkel, salon, toko pakaian kecil, galeri seni, dan lain-lain? 
Jika demikian, Anda mungkin telah menemukan diri Anda menghabiskan BANYAK WAKTU browsing Web membangun sebuah file prospek. Surel, situs web, alamat, dan nomor telepon tersebar di mana-mana, dan, jika bukan seorang magang, ANDA akan harus menghabiskan waktu berharga mengumpulkannya sebelum Anda bahkan bisa memulai prospek. 
Ini adalah versi modern dari "Ambil buku telepon, pergi ke 'A' dan mulai menelepon". 
Apa yang Dimaksud dengan "FEATURES"?
Dengan menggunakan perangkat lunak dan data dari peta, Anda dapat: 
* Menemukan lead secara literal di mana saja di dunia 
* Dengan cepat menyaring dan menganalisis lead di Excel

WHAT

Presto Map lead extractor helps you extract business listings from Bing Maps and OpenStreetMap.

FOR WHOM AND WHY

Is your business targeting small businesses: Restaurants, bars, grocery stores, garages, hairdressers, small clothing shops, art galleries, and so on?

If that's the case, you've probably found yourself spending COUNTLESS hours browsing the Web building a prospection file. Emails, websites, addresses, and phone numbers are scattered all over the place, and, if not an intern, YOU will have to spend precious time gathering them before you can even get started prospecting.

This is the modern equivalent of "Take the phone book, go to 'A' and start dialing".

FEATURES

Using this software and data from maps, you can:
* Find leads literally at any place in the world
* Quickly filter and analyze leads in Excel 

The app is not magic. It extracts all available data from Online maps. Without this software, you can do it manually or hire a virtual assistant to do this job.

Functionality:
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Bing maps 
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Open Street maps (OSM) 
ğŸ“Š Download as Excel with proper column types or in CSV
âœ¨ The resulting spreadsheet contains 22 columns including phone numbers, venue name, and address (both English and localized variants), website, average rating, etc.

Please note: this app is freemium software. You can use a limited version for free or upgrade for unlimited usage. The download feature is limited to the recent 40 records. 

NOW TO USE ON BING MAPS

1. Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2. Search for something on Bing Maps - http://bing.com/maps/
3. See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
4. Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup

NOW TO USE ON OPEN STREET MAPS

1) Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2) Go to https://overpass-turbo.eu/ 
You can use any Oversee gateway - https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API 
3) Perform search by pressing â€œRunâ€ - the query language is described there: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API
4) See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
5) Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup
5.1) Clear results if you donâ€™t need them and want to collect from scratch

ISSUES

If you see that your queries are slow on the web it could break Presto functionality.

GET SUPPORT

Support email: support@presto-maps-scraper.com

DISCLAIMER

The OpenStreemMap is a trademark of the OpenStreetMap Foundation, and is used with their permission.
This product are not endorsed by or affiliated with the OpenStreetMap Foundation.

The Bing is a trademark of the Microsoft Corporation. This product are not endorsed by or affiliated with the Microsoft Corporation.

long.lt:
WHAT

Presto Map lead extractor helps you extract business listings from Bing Maps and OpenStreetMap.

FOR WHOM AND WHY

Is your business targeting small businesses: Restaurants, bars, grocery stores, garages, hairdressers, small clothing shops, art galleries, and so on?

If that's the case, you've probably found yourself spending COUNTLESS hours browsing the Web building a prospection file. Emails, websites, addresses, and phone numbers are scattered all over the place, and, if not an intern, YOU will have to spend precious time gathering them before you can even get started prospecting.

This is the modern equivalent of "Take the phone book, go to 'A' and start dialing".

FEATURES

Using this software and data from maps, you can:
* Find leads literally at any place in the world
* Quickly filter and analyze leads in Excel 

The app is not magic. It extracts all available data from Online maps. Without this software, you can do it manually or hire a virtual assistant to do this job.

Functionality:
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Bing maps 
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Open Street maps (OSM) 
ğŸ“Š Download as Excel with proper column types or in CSV
âœ¨ The resulting spreadsheet contains 22 columns including phone numbers, venue name, and address (both English and localized variants), website, average rating, etc.

Please note: this app is freemium software. You can use a limited version for free or upgrade for unlimited usage. The download feature is limited to the recent 40 records. 

NOW TO USE ON BING MAPS

1. Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2. Search for something on Bing Maps - http://bing.com/maps/
3. See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
4. Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup

NOW TO USE ON OPEN STREET MAPS

1) Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2) Go to https://overpass-turbo.eu/ 
You can use any Oversee gateway - https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API 
3) Perform search by pressing â€œRunâ€ - the query language is described there: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API
4) See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
5) Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup
5.1) Clear results if you donâ€™t need them and want to collect from scratch

ISSUES

If you see that your queries are slow on the web it could break Presto functionality.

GET SUPPORT

Support email: support@presto-maps-scraper.com

DISCLAIMER

The OpenStreemMap is a trademark of the OpenStreetMap Foundation, and is used with their permission.
This product are not endorsed by or affiliated with the OpenStreetMap Foundation.

The Bing is a trademark of the Microsoft Corporation. This product are not endorsed by or affiliated with the Microsoft Corporation.

Presto Map Lead Extractor adalah alat bantu yang membantu anda mengekstrak senarai perniagaan dari OpenStreetMap. Untuk Siapa Dan Mengapa?
Adakah perniagaan anda menargetkan syarikat kecil: Restoran, bar, kedai runcit, kereta, penyunting rambut, kedai pakaian kecil, galeri seni, dan sebagainya? Jika demikian, anda mungkin telah menemui diri anda menghabiskan BERJAM-JAM melayari Web membina fail prospeksi. E-mel, laman web, alamat dan nombor telefon tersebar di seluruh tempat, dan, jika tidak ada intern, ANDA akan perlu menghabiskan masa yang berharga mengumpulkan mereka sebelum anda boleh bermula memprospek.
Ini adalah ekvivalen moden dari "Ambil buku telefon, pergi ke 'A' dan mula menghubungi".
Ciri-ciri
Dengan perisian dan data ini anda boleh:
* Cari peluang secara literal di mana sahaja di dunia
* Menapis dan menganalisis dengan cepat peluang dalam Excel
Aplikasi ini bukanlah sihir. Ia mengekstrak semua data yang tersedia dari peta dalam talian. Tanpa perisian ini, anda boleh melakukannya secara manual atau menyewa seorang pekerja bantuan maya untuk melakukan kerja ini.
Kesederhanaan:
ğŸ“ Ektract senarai dari Open Street Maps (OSM) 
ğŸ“Š Muat turun sebagai Excel dengan jenis lajur yang betul atau dalam CSV
âœ¨ Lembar kerja yang dihasilkan mengandungi 22 lajur termasuk nombor telefon, nama tempat, dan alamat (baik variasi Bahasa Inggeris dan berbahasa lokal), laman web, purata penarafan, dan lain-lain.
Sila ambil perhatian: aplikasi ini adalah perisian freemium. Anda boleh menggunakan versi terhad secara percuma atau naik taraf untuk penggunaan tanpa had. Ciri muat turun adalah terhad kepada 40 rekod terkini.
SEKARANG UNTUK MENGGUNAKAN
1) Klik pada ikon "puzzle" di toolbar. Cari ikon Presto dan pin ke toolbar untuk akses pantas.
2) Pergi ke https://overpass-turbo.eu/ 
Anda boleh menggunakan mana-mana gateway Oversee - https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API 
3) Lakukan carian dengan menekan "Run" - bahasa pertanyaan ini dijelaskan di sana: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API
4) Lihat bilangan keputusan bertambah di atas ikon toolbar
5) Muat turun semua rekod yang dikumpulkan dengan mengklik butang "Muat turun rekod" di popup ekstensi
5.1) Padamkan keputusan jika anda tidak memerlukannya dan mahu mengumpulkan semula dari awal
ISU
Jika anda melihat bahawa pertanyaan anda lambat di web, ia boleh memecahkan fungsi Presto.
DAPATKAN SOKONGAN
E-mel sokongan: support@presto-maps-scraper.com
NOTIS
OpenStreetMap adalah tanda dagangan OpenStreetMap Foundation, dan digunakan dengan kebenaran mereka.
Produk ini tidak mendapat sokongan atau berafiliasi dengan OpenStreetMap Foundation.

WHAT

Presto Map lead extractor helps you extract business listings from Bing Maps and OpenStreetMap.

FOR WHOM AND WHY

Is your business targeting small businesses: Restaurants, bars, grocery stores, garages, hairdressers, small clothing shops, art galleries, and so on?

If that's the case, you've probably found yourself spending COUNTLESS hours browsing the Web building a prospection file. Emails, websites, addresses, and phone numbers are scattered all over the place, and, if not an intern, YOU will have to spend precious time gathering them before you can even get started prospecting.

This is the modern equivalent of "Take the phone book, go to 'A' and start dialing".

FEATURES

Using this software and data from maps, you can:
* Find leads literally at any place in the world
* Quickly filter and analyze leads in Excel 

The app is not magic. It extracts all available data from Online maps. Without this software, you can do it manually or hire a virtual assistant to do this job.

Functionality:
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Bing maps 
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Open Street maps (OSM) 
ğŸ“Š Download as Excel with proper column types or in CSV
âœ¨ The resulting spreadsheet contains 22 columns including phone numbers, venue name, and address (both English and localized variants), website, average rating, etc.

Please note: this app is freemium software. You can use a limited version for free or upgrade for unlimited usage. The download feature is limited to the recent 40 records. 

NOW TO USE ON BING MAPS

1. Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2. Search for something on Bing Maps - http://bing.com/maps/
3. See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
4. Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup

NOW TO USE ON OPEN STREET MAPS

1) Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2) Go to https://overpass-turbo.eu/ 
You can use any Oversee gateway - https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API 
3) Perform search by pressing â€œRunâ€ - the query language is described there: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API
4) See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
5) Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup
5.1) Clear results if you donâ€™t need them and want to collect from scratch

ISSUES

If you see that your queries are slow on the web it could break Presto functionality.

GET SUPPORT

Support email: support@presto-maps-scraper.com

DISCLAIMER

The OpenStreemMap is a trademark of the OpenStreetMap Foundation, and is used with their permission.
This product are not endorsed by or affiliated with the OpenStreetMap Foundation.

The Bing is a trademark of the Microsoft Corporation. This product are not endorsed by or affiliated with the Microsoft Corporation.

Presto Map lead extractor adalah alat yang membantu anda mengekstrak senarai perniagaan dari OpenStreetMap. Untuk Siapa dan Mengapa? Adakah perniagaan anda menjangkau perniagaan kecil: Restoran, bar, kedai runcit, kereta basuh, jurufoto, kedai pakaian kecil, galeri seni dan sebagainya? Jika begitu, anda mungkin telah menemui diri anda menghabiskan BANYAK jam membaca Web membina fail prospek. E-mel, laman web, alamat dan nombor telefon tersebar di mana-mana, dan, jika bukan seorang intern, ANDA akan perlu menghabiskan masa yang berharga untuk mengumpulkan mereka sebelum anda boleh bermula memprospek. Ini adalah versi moden dari "Ambil buku telefon, pergi ke 'A' dan mula menelefon".
Ciri-ciri: Dengan perisian dan data ini, anda boleh:
* Cari keutamaan hampir di mana sahaja di dunia
* Menapis dan menganalisis dengan cepat keutamaan dalam Excel 
Aplikasi ini bukanlah sihir. Ia mengekstrak semua data yang ada dari Peta Dalam Talian. Tanpa perisian ini, anda boleh melakukannya secara manual atau menyewa seorang juruwang maya untuk melakukan kerja ini.
Fungsionaliti:
ğŸ“ Ektrak senarai dari Peta Jalan Buka (OSM) 
ğŸ“Š Muat turun sebagai Excel dengan jenis lajur yang betul atau dalam CSV
âœ¨ Spreadsheet yang dihasilkan mengandungi 22 lajur termasuk nombor telefon, nama tempat, dan alamat (kedua-dua varian Inggeris dan berbahasa setempat), laman web, purata penarafan, dan lain-lain.
Sila ambil perhatian: aplikasi ini adalah perisian freemium. Anda boleh menggunakan versi terhad untuk percuma atau naik taraf untuk penggunaan tidak terhad. Ciri muat turun terhad kepada 40 rekod terkini. 
Kini untuk menggunakannya:
1) Klik pada ikon "puzzle" di toolbar. Cari ikon Presto dan pin ke toolbar untuk akses pantas.
2) Pergi ke https://overpass-turbo.eu/ 
Anda boleh menggunakan mana-mana gateway Oversee - https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API 
3) Lakukan carian dengan menekan "Run" - bahasa pertanyaan itu dijelaskan di sana: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API
4) Lihat bilangan hasil meningkat di atas ikon toolbar
5) Muat turun semua rekod yang dikumpulkan dengan mengklik butang "Muat turun rekod" dalam popup ekstensi
5.1) Padamkan hasil jika anda tidak memerlukannya dan mahu mengumpulkan dari awal
Isu: Jika anda melihat pertanyaan anda lambat di web, ia boleh memecahkan fungsi Presto.
Dapatkan Sokongan:
E-mel Sokongan: support@presto-maps-scraper.com
Penafian:
OpenStreetMap adalah tanda dagangan OpenStreetMap Foundation, dan digunakan dengan kebenarannya. Produk ini tidak diendors oleh atau berafiliasi dengan OpenStreetMap Foundation.

Presto Map Lead Extractor helpt je bedrijvenlijsten te extraheren uit OpenStreetMap.
VOOR WIE EN WAAROM
Is jouw bedrijf gericht op kleine bedrijven: restaurants, bars, supermarkten, garages, kappers, kleine kledingwinkels, kunstgalerijen, enzovoort? 
Als dat het geval is, heb je waarschijnlijk tal van uren besteed aan het doorzoeken van het web om een prospectief bestand samen te stellen. E-mails, websites, adressen en telefoonnummers zijn overal verspreid, en als je geen stagiair bent, zul JIJ waardevolle tijd moeten besteden aan het verzamelen ervan voordat je aan de slag kunt gaan met prospecteren.
Dit is de moderne equivalent van "Haal de telefoongids, ga naar 'A' en begin te bellen".
FUNCTIONALITEITEN
Met behulp van deze software en gegevens uit kaarten kun je:
* Leads letterlijk op elke plek ter wereld vinden
* Leads snel filteren en analyseren in Excel
De app is geen tovermiddel. Het extraheert alle beschikbare gegevens uit Online kaarten. Zonder deze software kun je het handmatig doen of een virtuele assistent inhuren om deze taak uit te voeren.
Functionaliteit:
ğŸ“ Extraheer lijsten uit Open Street maps (OSM) 
ğŸ“Š Download als Excel met juiste kolomtypes of in CSV
âœ¨ De resulterende spreadsheet bevat 22 kolommen, waaronder telefoonnummers, naam van de locatie en adres (zowel Engelse als lokalisatievarianten), website, gemiddelde beoordeling, enz.
Let op: deze app is freemium software. U kunt een beperkte versie gratis gebruiken of upgraden voor onbeperkt gebruik. Het downloaden is beperkt tot de recente 40 records.
NU GEBRUIKEN
1) Klik op het "puzzel" -pictogram in de werkbalk. Zoek Presto's pictogram en pin het op de werkbalk voor snelle toegang.
2) Ga naar https://overpass-turbo.eu/ 
U kunt elke Oversee gateway gebruiken - https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API 
3) Voer de zoekopdracht uit door op "Run" te klikken - de query-taal wordt daar beschreven: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API
4) Zie het aantal resultaten toenemen boven het pictogram van de werkbalk
5) Download alle verzamelde records door op de knop "Records downloaden" te klikken in het pop-upvenster van de extensie
5.1) Wis de resultaten als je ze niet nodig hebt en vanaf het begin wilt verzamelen
PROBLEMEN
Als je ziet dat je queries traag zijn op het web, kan dit de functionaliteit van Presto verstoren.
ONDERSTEUNING KRIJGEN
Ondersteunings-e-mail: support@presto-maps-scraper.com
AANSPRAKELIJKHEID
OpenStreetMap is een handelsmerk van de OpenStreetMap Foundation en wordt gebruikt met hun toestemming.
Dit product is niet goedgekeurd of aangesloten bij de OpenStreetMap Foundation.

WHAT

Presto Map lead extractor helps you extract business listings from Bing Maps and OpenStreetMap.

FOR WHOM AND WHY

Is your business targeting small businesses: Restaurants, bars, grocery stores, garages, hairdressers, small clothing shops, art galleries, and so on?

If that's the case, you've probably found yourself spending COUNTLESS hours browsing the Web building a prospection file. Emails, websites, addresses, and phone numbers are scattered all over the place, and, if not an intern, YOU will have to spend precious time gathering them before you can even get started prospecting.

This is the modern equivalent of "Take the phone book, go to 'A' and start dialing".

FEATURES

Using this software and data from maps, you can:
* Find leads literally at any place in the world
* Quickly filter and analyze leads in Excel 

The app is not magic. It extracts all available data from Online maps. Without this software, you can do it manually or hire a virtual assistant to do this job.

Functionality:
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Bing maps 
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Open Street maps (OSM) 
ğŸ“Š Download as Excel with proper column types or in CSV
âœ¨ The resulting spreadsheet contains 22 columns including phone numbers, venue name, and address (both English and localized variants), website, average rating, etc.

Please note: this app is freemium software. You can use a limited version for free or upgrade for unlimited usage. The download feature is limited to the recent 40 records. 

NOW TO USE ON BING MAPS

1. Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2. Search for something on Bing Maps - http://bing.com/maps/
3. See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
4. Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup

NOW TO USE ON OPEN STREET MAPS

1) Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2) Go to https://overpass-turbo.eu/ 
You can use any Oversee gateway - https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API 
3) Perform search by pressing â€œRunâ€ - the query language is described there: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API
4) See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
5) Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup
5.1) Clear results if you donâ€™t need them and want to collect from scratch

ISSUES

If you see that your queries are slow on the web it could break Presto functionality.

GET SUPPORT

Support email: support@presto-maps-scraper.com

WHAT

Presto Map lead extractor helps you extract business listings from Bing Maps and OpenStreetMap.

FOR WHOM AND WHY

Is your business targeting small businesses: Restaurants, bars, grocery stores, garages, hairdressers, small clothing shops, art galleries, and so on?

If that's the case, you've probably found yourself spending COUNTLESS hours browsing the Web building a prospection file. Emails, websites, addresses, and phone numbers are scattered all over the place, and, if not an intern, YOU will have to spend precious time gathering them before you can even get started prospecting.

This is the modern equivalent of "Take the phone book, go to 'A' and start dialing".

FEATURES

Using this software and data from maps, you can:
* Find leads literally at any place in the world
* Quickly filter and analyze leads in Excel 

The app is not magic. It extracts all available data from Online maps. Without this software, you can do it manually or hire a virtual assistant to do this job.

Functionality:
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Bing maps 
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Open Street maps (OSM) 
ğŸ“Š Download as Excel with proper column types or in CSV
âœ¨ The resulting spreadsheet contains 22 columns including phone numbers, venue name, and address (both English and localized variants), website, average rating, etc.

Please note: this app is freemium software. You can use a limited version for free or upgrade for unlimited usage. The download feature is limited to the recent 40 records. 

NOW TO USE ON BING MAPS

1. Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2. Search for something on Bing Maps - http://bing.com/maps/
3. See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
4. Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup

NOW TO USE ON OPEN STREET MAPS

1) Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2) Go to https://overpass-turbo.eu/ 
You can use any Oversee gateway - https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API 
3) Perform search by pressing â€œRunâ€ - the query language is described there: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API
4) See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
5) Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup
5.1) Clear results if you donâ€™t need them and want to collect from scratch

ISSUES

If you see that your queries are slow on the web it could break Presto functionality.

GET SUPPORT

Support email: support@presto-maps-scraper.com

WHAT

Presto Map lead extractor helps you extract business listings from Bing Maps and OpenStreetMap.

FOR WHOM AND WHY

Is your business targeting small businesses: Restaurants, bars, grocery stores, garages, hairdressers, small clothing shops, art galleries, and so on?

If that's the case, you've probably found yourself spending COUNTLESS hours browsing the Web building a prospection file. Emails, websites, addresses, and phone numbers are scattered all over the place, and, if not an intern, YOU will have to spend precious time gathering them before you can even get started prospecting.

This is the modern equivalent of "Take the phone book, go to 'A' and start dialing".

FEATURES

Using this software and data from maps, you can:
* Find leads literally at any place in the world
* Quickly filter and analyze leads in Excel 

The app is not magic. It extracts all available data from Online maps. Without this software, you can do it manually or hire a virtual assistant to do this job.

Functionality:
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Bing maps 
ğŸ“ Extract listings from Open Street maps (OSM) 
ğŸ“Š Download as Excel with proper column types or in CSV
âœ¨ The resulting spreadsheet contains 22 columns including phone numbers, venue name, and address (both English and localized variants), website, average rating, etc.

Please note: this app is freemium software. You can use a limited version for free or upgrade for unlimited usage. The download feature is limited to the recent 40 records. 

NOW TO USE ON BING MAPS

1. Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2. Search for something on Bing Maps - http://bing.com/maps/
3. See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
4. Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup

NOW TO USE ON OPEN STREET MAPS

1) Click on the â€œpuzzleâ€ icon at the toolbar. Find Prestoâ€™s icon and pin to the toolbar for quick access.
2) Go to https://overpass-turbo.eu/ 
You can use any Oversee gateway - https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API 
3) Perform search by pressing â€œRunâ€ - the query language is described there: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Overpass_API
4) See the number of results increasing over the toolbar icon
5) Download all records collected by clicking the â€œDownload recordsâ€ button in the extensionâ€™s popup
5.1) Clear results if you donâ€™t need them and want to collect from scratch

ISSUES

If you see that your queries are slow on the web it could break Presto functionality.

GET SUPPORT

Support email: support@presto-maps-scraper.com

FOR WHOM AND WHY

Is your business targeting small businesses: Restaurants, bars, grocery stores, garages, hairdressers, small clothing shops, art galleries, and so on?

If that's the case, you've probably found yourself spending COUNTLESS hours browsing the Web building a prospection file. Emails, websites, addresses, and phone numbers are scattered all over the place, and, if not an intern, YOU will have to spend precious time gathering them before you can even get started prospecting.

This is the modern equivalent of "Take the phone book, go to 'A' and start dialing".

FEATURES

Using this software and data from maps, you can:
* Find leads literally at any place in the world
* Quickly filter and analyze leads in Excel 

The app is not magic. It extracts all available data from Online maps. Without this software, you can do it manually or hire a virtual assistant to do this job.
